{"id": "art-143", "label": "Art. 143", "title": "Art. 143", "slug": "art-143", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 143 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1001599054\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2203\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1001599054\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\npoate delega conducerea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> unuia\nsau mai multor directori, numind pe unul dintre ei director general.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1442538902\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2202\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1442538902\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Directorii pot fi <span class=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span>\ndintre administratori sau din afara consiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1381992437\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2201\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1381992437\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dac&#259; prin actul constitutiv sau printr-o\nhot&#259;râre a adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nse prevede acest lucru, <span class=SpellE>pre&#351;edintele</span> consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npoate fi numit <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> director general.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1432590449\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2200\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1432590449\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)În cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> ale c&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ii</span>\nfinanciare anuale fac obiectul unei <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>\nlegale de auditare financiar&#259;, delegarea conducerii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nîn conformitate cu alin. (1) este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_916127403\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2199\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_916127403\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În <span class=SpellE>în&#355;elesul</span> prezentei <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legi</i>, director al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> este numai acea persoan&#259;\nc&#259;reia i-au fost delegate <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;ii</span> de\nconducere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, în conformitate cu\nalin. (1). Orice alt&#259; persoan&#259;, indiferent de denumirea tehnic&#259;\na postului ocupat în cadrul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\neste exclus&#259; de la aplicarea normelor prezentei <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legi</i> cu privire la directorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}